name: Promo for Propinquity
description:
ethereal_interface will release track #3 "Propinquity" of their visual album dream_logs on Thursday November 4th at 3pm eastern time. 30 editions for 2 tezos. This is the promo to celebrate and remind you of the track 3 release! See you there :)
